/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:27:The mission context is stronger than "the candidate uses an exact NS-looking feature." Tao's result blocks anything resting only on energy identity plus standard harmonic analysis. So the chain should demand a concrete statement of what the averaged model destroys and where that destruction enters the estimate. As written, a candidate can survive Step 1 by sounding algebraically special without showing that the specialness survives localization and actually matters quantitatively.
