/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/selected/chain-01.md:27:- Kill condition: if no candidate is both estimate-relevant and plausibly nontrivial under the Tao filter, stop immediately and write the obstruction memo.
