/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/mission-context.md:333:- Action: name the candidate NS-specific ingredient if one exists, and separate it from generic harmonic facts that Tao's averaged model should preserve.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/mission-context.md:444:What Tao's averaged model preserves for present purposes:
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-002/GOAL.md:43:- Be explicit about what Tao's averaged model preserves and therefore what it does not kill.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:5:The attacker is mostly correct. The original chain had real discipline compared with many speculative symbol-level programs: it fixed a narrow object class, imposed kill conditions, and explicitly worried about the usual failure mode that triad-level elegance disappears once one reconstructs the full equation. But it still left too much freedom early, especially around the theorem endpoint, the meaning of a "gain," and the quantitative size of any alleged helical advantage.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:7:The strongest repair is not to discard the chain. It is to flip its default posture. This branch should be run as an obstruction-first helical-symbol program whose positive branch survives only if one exact feature can be written as an explicit candidate inequality and still wins after dyadic summation, mixed-helicity restoration, and any needed localization.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:21:The attacker is right that a ledger of helicity signs, resonance classes, and Leray-symbol identities is cheap unless it is tied to the sign, size, or summability of a specific term in a specific estimate. The original chain also left "Tao-sensitive" too informal. The refined chain keeps the ledger but makes it operational: each promoted feature must be attached to the chosen estimate and assigned a maximal plausible quantitative effect before full reconstruction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:27:Difference from an averaged model is not evidence of theorem relevance by itself. The original chain treated this distinction as more probative than it really is. The refined chain demotes it to a secondary discriminator: useful only after the feature has already shown potential leverage on the fixed bottleneck term under a precisely stated comparison class.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:41:### 6. Restricted favorable triad families are a cherry-picking loophole unless they carry quantified mass of the relevant transfer
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:45:Correct. In this subject the best-looking same-helicity or near-resonant sectors are often exactly where full-equation relevance is weakest. The refined chain therefore requires any restricted interaction class to come with a quantified share of the relevant transfer or shell sum. Otherwise the branch dies as a regime artifact.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:47:### 7. Step 4 must explicitly charge dyadic summation, angular multiplicity, mixed-helicity restoration, and localization losses
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:51:This is the strongest criticism and the core of the refined chain. "Charge the full cost" was directionally right but too rhetorical. The revised version requires an explicit reconstruction ledger that includes shell summation, angular multiplicity, non-favorable triads, and localization or commutator losses when the theorem target needs them.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:71:3. It forces Step 3 to write one explicit candidate inequality and quantify the relevance of any restricted triad family.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:72:4. It turns Step 4 into a concrete reconstruction bill covering dyadic, angular, mixed-helicity, and localization losses.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:81:- The negative branch is strong and honest. A precise obstruction saying exact helical-triad structure does not survive shell summation, mixed-helicity restoration, or localization is a presentable outcome.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/selector.md:15:   - It opens the invariant/cascade side of the search space, is not a replay of the LEI rewrite audit, and can still close with a clean no-go about mixed-helicity restoration, localization, or regime-artifact failure.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/selector.md:34:- **Useful output on failure is strongest here:** Chain 01 yields a reusable property atlas, Chain 02 yields a precise material-obstruction ledger, and Chain 03 yields a sharp verdict on whether joint energy-helicity geometry has real theorem-level bite beyond folklore.
