/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-04.md:5:Viscosity does not destroy transport structure completely; it replaces deterministic Kelvin/Cauchy laws with stochastic transport identities. This chain asks whether one exact stochastic circulation or back-to-label object yields theorem-relevant control that Tao's averaged model would not preserve.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-04.md:39:- Action: specify exactly what the averaged model should fail to preserve:
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-03.md:16:This chain is tensorial and stretching-first. It does not assume blowup, does not work at triad-symbol level, and does not begin from coherent-structure geometry. It targets the exact local-to-nonlocal tensor mechanism directly.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/planner-chains/chain-03.md:41:- Action: for each shortlisted observable, state exactly what should fail in Tao's averaged model: sign coupling, frame coherence, cancellation, or another named mechanism.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-02.md:5:The exact NS transport/stretching law may become usable only in material variables. Instead of trying to beat an Eulerian estimate, this chain asks whether cumulative deformation, singular-value growth, or one material stretching observable yields a continuation criterion or contradiction pathway that Tao's averaged model would not preserve.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-02.md:43:- Action: state precisely which part of the structure the averaged model should destroy:
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-01.md:5:The mission may be closer to a publishable obstruction map than to a single proof architecture. The right first branch is therefore a direct comparison between exact Navier-Stokes and Tao's averaged model, updated by all prior run negatives, with promotion only for properties that are both genuinely destroyed by averaging and operational at one named theorem endpoint.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-01.md:44:  joint energy-helicity transfer,
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:3:This chain has one genuine strength: it correctly identifies a real discriminator, namely whether there is any exact Navier-Stokes triad-level structure that a Tao-style averaging would wash out. That is a legitimate fault line.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:11:- The choice set is too broad. "Helical decomposition," "triad-symbol coefficients," shell flux, enstrophy production, stretching transfer, sign, cancellation, coercive depletion, and derivative-count improvement are not comparable objects. A branch can survive by picking the easiest symbolic package and the softest notion of gain.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:13:- The kill condition only guards against drifting across architectures. It does not guard against cherry-picking within the architecture. A branch can stay fully inside "triad geometry" and still opportunistically choose whichever bottleneck/gain pair makes the memo sound best.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:14:- There is no quantitative threshold for what would count as a meaningful gain. A sign on a sparse triad class, a cancellation that loses under shell multiplicity, and a derivative improvement too small to close any estimate are all currently allowed to look live.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:18:## Step 2 - Build the exact triad ledger and the Tao comparator
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:22:- The "Tao comparator" is not fixed tightly enough. Which averaged model, preserving which invariants, at which comparison granularity? Without that, "Tao-sensitive" can become a rhetorical label instead of a mathematically checkable distinction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:24:- The step ignores the possibility that the attractive structure is exact at the single-triad level but irrelevant once conjugation symmetry, multiplicity, and cross-class compensation are included. That is precisely the trap in this area.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:27:Net: this step can produce a sharp-looking triad ledger while still failing to identify anything that survives honest comparison or invariant reformulation.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:29:## Step 3 - Attach one promoted triad feature to one theorem gap
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:34:- Restricting to one promoted mechanism is good discipline, but it happens too late. The prior-art benchmark should come before promotion, not after. Otherwise the chain can spend time promoting a mechanism that is just a repackaging of Waleffe-type helical interaction lore, Beltrami depletion rhetoric, or decimated-shell intuition.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:40:## Step 4 - Stress-test shell summation, bad triads, and localization debt
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:42:This is the step where most triad-geometry ideas die, and the chain understates how terminal that is.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:44:- The route postpones the hardest issues until after mechanism promotion. That is backwards. Shell multiplicity, nonlocal triads, and physical-space reconstruction are not cleanup details; they are the main obstruction.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:45:- "Restore the full triad sum" is the real proof problem, but the chain gives no criterion for what would count as surviving it. Without an explicit summability target, a favorable-sign subset can look encouraging even when it is drowned by the rest of the ledger.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:46:- Bad-triad contamination is treated as one item on a checklist, but in practice it can dominate. Unless there is a counting lemma, a weight, or a coercive imbalance proving favorable classes beat unfavorable ones, the whole mechanism is likely cosmetic.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:47:- Nonlocal triads are named but not structurally handled. That is a serious omission, because many shell-local heuristics collapse precisely when high-low and nonlocal interactions are put back in.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:57:- A "proposition-scale target" sounds rigorous, but a proposition can still be mathematically true and strategically useless. The chain should require that the first missing lemma plausibly advances the mission rather than merely isolating a decorative triad effect.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:58:- The negative endpoint is better than nothing, but it still risks being too coarse. There is a difference between "single-triad signal does not survive shell summation," "survives on a sparse class but loses to multiplicity," and "requires localization whose cost exceeds the gain." Those are materially different obstructions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:59:- The final kill condition only bans vague language like "favorable triads" or "special cancellations." That is good housekeeping, but it is not enough. The branch should also have to freeze constants, interaction classes, and the exact summation regime under which the claim is supposed to matter.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:65:- The central premise is already biased. It assumes that if Tao-style averaging destroys a decisive structure, the "sharpest candidate" is exact triad-symbol or helical geometry. That is a strong prior, not an established fact. Other exact structures could be more decisive: pressure coupling, incompressibility constraints in physical space, or localization/intermittency interactions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:67:- The route is highly exposed to prior-art overlap. Helical-sign classes, Beltrami depletion, restricted interaction geometry, and shell-transfer rhetoric have been mined for years. The chain recognizes this, but too late. The literature filter should be front-loaded, not attached after mechanism promotion.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:68:- The kill-condition calibration is uneven. Early steps are permissive enough that weak ideas can survive, while later steps can kill a route only after substantial memo-writing. Conversely, a failure on one frozen bottleneck may not actually show the broader triad route is dead; it may just show that the chosen bottleneck was the wrong test case. The chain does not separate those two failure modes cleanly.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:70:- The chain is structurally tempted to overvalue exactness. Exact symbolic structure is not the same thing as usable coercivity. Many exact triad identities are mathematically real and strategically irrelevant.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-02.md:76:But as written, the route is still too easy to keep alive with elegant symbolic bookkeeping, and too hard to force into a theorem-relevant estimate. The most likely failure mode is not that the triad geometry is false; it is that it is exact, interesting, and ultimately cosmetic once the full equation is restored.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:5:The true 3D Navier-Stokes nonlinearity transports both energy and helicity. The live question is whether this coupled invariant geometry yields a theorem-relevant depletion or no-bad-cascade statement that is invisible to energy-only flux rewrites and stronger than the old symbol-first triad folklore.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:11:- one conditional coupled-flux statement tying a specific energy-helicity transfer observable to a continuation criterion, concentration exclusion, or stretching/enstrophy bottleneck; or
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:12:- a calibrated obstruction memo showing that the apparent gain dies first by mixed-helicity restoration,
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:19:This chain is invariant and cascade-facing. It is not another LEI-flux rewrite audit and not another pure helical-triad sign ledger. Its core object is the joint energy-helicity budget of the full equation.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:29:  or a contradiction line for concentrated helicity-bearing regions.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:33:  or another sharply defined joint energy-helicity ledger.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:34:- Action: ban pure energy-flux reformulations and pure same-helicity folklore as standalone success criteria.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:41:- Action: write the exact energy and helicity transfer identities in the chosen package, marking which parts are exact NS structure and which are only bookkeeping.
