/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:46:- Action: reject candidates whose distinction from the averaged model is only a change of decomposition.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:48:- Kill condition: if the coupled package collapses to energy-only control or a repackaged triad sign table, close the chain negatively.
