/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:65:- Action: restore mixed-helicity interactions, low-helicity regions, viscosity, pressure, and any localization losses required by the chosen endpoint.
