/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/planner-chains/chain-03.md:84:- Kill condition: if the final claim can be read as "helicity is interesting," the chain has not earned promotion.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:5:This chain is disciplined about one real danger: accidentally reviving the dead De Giorgi machinery under Lorentz-space language. That is its best feature. Its main weakness is deeper: weak-type or Lorentz structure is a norm package, not an evident Navier-Stokes-specific mechanism. Under the mission's own Tao filter, that is a serious problem from the start, because weak-type Calderon-Zygmund, interpolation, and endpoint singular-integral technology are exactly the sort of harmonic-analysis assets the averaged model is meant to preserve.
