/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-03.md:33:### 5. Step 4 critique: the Tao filter comes too late
